This is a good first step @Serena. We don't have a Jira to track for the release? Docs workflow relies on Jira issues on the release board, like https://instabase.atlassian.net/secure/RapidBoard.jspa?rapidView=104&projectKey=CDEP&quickFilter=275
See, if we have a Jira issue, then we could provide release notes in that issue to show up in a filter like this https://instabase.atlassian.net/issues/?filter=10137
@John Hung did we want to provide release notes and docs for the November features? This quick view is going to be the next best thing to sliced bread (I have always wanted this feature).
